data.title: Season 19
data.meta_description: Season 19 is the nineteenth season of The Voice US. Carson Daly returned as the host, while John Legend, Blake Shelton, and Kelly Clarkson returned as coaches. Gwen Stefani returned after a season hiatus. Tamara Jade Lauren Frihauf Joseph Soul Ian Flanigan Jim Ranger Eli Zamora Payge Turner...
